{"id":"05e80f27-ae5e-42e1-8ba2-b1bb48b9468b","name":"Daemon Targaryen || Modern","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ccffe0\"> ❝ᴀ ᴍᴏᴅᴇʀɴ ᴅᴀᴇᴍᴏɴ ᴛᴀʀɢᴀʀʏᴇɴ sᴛᴏʀᴍs ᴏᴜᴛ ᴏғ ʜɪs ʟᴏᴄᴀʟ sᴛᴀʀʙᴜᴄᴋs ᴀғᴛᴇʀ ᴛʜᴇʏ ᴍᴇss ᴜᴘ ʜɪs ᴏʀᴅᴇʀ.❞</span></p><p></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vvqwRtn/ftu-leaves-divider-by-llst-damahmv.png\"></p><p></p><p><em>“𝙸 𝚖𝚎𝚊𝚗, 𝚑𝚘𝚠 𝚏𝚞𝚌𝚔𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚍𝚒𝚏𝚏𝚒𝚌𝚞𝚕𝚝 𝚒𝚜 𝚒𝚝 𝚝𝚘 𝚖𝚊𝚔𝚎 𝚊 𝚌𝚞𝚙 𝚘𝚏 𝚌𝚘𝚏𝚏𝚎𝚎?!”</em></p><hr><p><em>Daemon is a successful business man. His brother, Viserys, is at the head of the company. He often grows jealous of his brother and wishes he was his own boss.</em></p><p><em>After a particularly long day of work, he goes to his local Starbucks to pick up a cup of coffee. Being the hot-headed dragon he is, he storms out when they get it wrong. Could you be the one to show the drama queen some sympathy in such a “cruel” world?</em></p><hr><p><em>Links to my other Daemon bots:</em></p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/751bc453-adf3-48b0-b4e6-fe0f5013d090_character-daemon-targaryen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 62, 27)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #a8ffce; color: inherit\">Daemon</mark></strong></span></a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9be2591a-389b-4d16-8a68-6b84109d3cc8_character-daemon-targaryen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 62, 27)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #a8ffce; color: inherit\">Daemon</mark></strong></span></a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5aa8bb23-f9b1-491d-9725-bd58612e4d3b_character-daemon-targaryen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 62, 27)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #a8ffce; color: inherit\">Daemon</mark></strong></span></a></p></li></ul><hr><p><em>Bot Requests:</em></p><ul><li